# AgToosa Handoff Rules

When executing `/agtoosa-handoff` or any handoff pack export, follow `Docs/AgToosa_Handoff.md` precisely.

- Reserved: `/agtoosa-handoff` and `agtoosa-handoff` names belong to AgToosa adapters only — do **not** route to `/create-skill`.
- On successful completion, print this line verbatim: `Next: /agtoosa-<command> — <rationale>` plus `SYNC:` pulse (see Lifecycle Next-Step Contract)
